[Note that DRC is included in the list of African countries with a measles alert, even though the outbreak is considered over and the number of cases in the country is decreasing [see next report]. This is because there continue to be high numbers of cases in the country, still presenting a risk to unvaccinated non-immune people. - Mod.LK

